data.description: Super cute ranch home! Sycamore Township services + Deer Park Schools + Rossmoyne taxes = the perfect trifecta and all close to Kenwood! Walk out to your relaxing deck in your parklike, fenced backyard. Double your living space in your professionally waterproofed basement. Original hardwood under carpet too! Long driveway offers plenty of off street parking! All appliances stay. Move right in and enjoy. Seller has purchased a one year home warranty for your peace of mind. (Agent is related to seller.)
